'''古風野牛'''（學名：'''''Bison antiquus'''''）是1萬年前[[更新世|更新世]]晚期時[[北美洲|北美洲]]最普遍的大型[[草食性|草食性]]動物，且是現存[[美洲野牛|美洲野牛]]的直接祖先<ref name="Tar Pits">{{cite web|title=Animals of the La Brea Tar Pits Timeline|url=http://www.tarpits.org/la-brea-tar-pits/timeline|website=La Brea Tar Pits & Museum|accessdate=14 March 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180111150652/http://www.tarpits.org/la-brea-tar-pits/timeline|archive-date=2018-01-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==描述==
[[File:Bison_antiquus_p1350762.jpg|thumb]]]]
[[西伯利亞野牛|西伯利亞野牛]]於[[更新世|更新世]][[冰河時期|冰河時期]]（大約 240,000 至 220,000 年前）<ref name="Belletal.2004">{{cite book | author = Bell, C.J. | year = 2004 |chapter= The Blancan, Irvingtonian, and Rancholabrean mammal ages |title=Late Cretaceous and Cenozoic Mammals of North America: Biostratigraphy and Geochronology |editor= Woodburne, M.O.| pages = 232–314 | location = New York | publisher = Columbia Univ. Press | isbn = 0-231-13040-6|display-authors=etal}}</ref><ref name="ScottandCox2008">{{cite book |author1=Scott, E. |author2=Cox, S.M. | year = 2008 |chapter=Late Pleistocene distribution of ''Bison'' (Mammalia; Artiodactyla) in the Mojave Desert of Southern California and Nevada |title=Geology and Vertebrate Paleontology of Western and Southern North America |editor1=Wang, X. |editor2=Barnes, L.G. | pages = 359–382 | location = Los Angeles | publisher = Natural History Museum of Los Angeles County}}</ref><ref name="Sandersetal.2009">{{cite book |author1=Sanders, A.E. |author2=R.E. Weems |author3=L.B. Albright III  |last-author-amp=yes | year = 2009 |chapter=Formalization of the mid-Pleistocene "Ten Mile Hill beds" in South Carolina with evidence for placement of the Irvingtonian–Rancholabrean boundary |title=Papers on Geology, Vertebrate Paleontology, and Biostratigraphy in Honor of Michael O. Woodburne |editor= Albright III, L.B. | pages = 369–375 | location = Flagstaff | publisher = Museum of Northern Arizona}}</ref>從[[西伯利亞|西伯利亞]]遷徙至[[阿拉斯加|阿拉斯加]]。西伯利亞野牛於300萬年前在北美洲發展成[[長角野牛|長角野牛]]。約距今2萬2千年前，長角野牛被古風野牛所取代。古風野牛於1萬8千年前開始大量繁殖，並於1萬年前與其他更新世大型動物群一同[[滅絕|滅絕]]<ref name="ScottandCox2008"/>，而在這之後美洲野牛出現，直到現今<ref name="Wilsonetal.2008">{{cite journal|author1=Wilson, M.C. |author2=L.V. Hills, B. Shapiro  |last-author-amp=yes |title=Late Pleistocene northward-dispersing ''Bison antiquus'' from the Bighill Creek Formation, Gallelli Gravel Pit, Alberta, Canada, and the fate of ''Bison occidentalis''|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_canadian-journal-of-earth-sciences_2008-07_45_7/page/827 |journal=Canadian Journal of Earth Sciences|volume=45|issue=7|pages=827–859|year=2008|doi = 10.1139/E08-027|bibcode = 2008CaJES..45..827W }}</ref>。古風野牛在[[拉布雷亞瀝青坑|拉布雷亞瀝青坑]]中是最為普遍的草食性動物<ref name="Tar Pits" />。

對比現今的[[美洲野牛屬|美洲野牛屬]]，古風野牛體型較高，骨頭及角較大。體型上較現存的美洲野牛大上 15-25% ，肩高可達 {{convert|2.27|m|ft|sp=us}}，體長可達 {{convert|4.6|m|ft|sp=us}}，體重則可達 {{convert|1588|kg|lb|sp=us}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.warkworthwesternweekend.com/competitors.php |title=存档副本 |access-date=2018-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110821104228/http://warkworthwesternweekend.com/competitors.php |archive-date=2011-08-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。古風野牛雙角角尖之間的距離約為 {{convert|1|m|ft|sp=us}}。



